## Frontend (Angular 21)
- Signals mandatory: signal(), computed(), effect() — never BehaviorSubject
- Injection: always inject(), never constructor injection
- HTTP: always RepoHttp (not HttpClient directly)
- Styles: CSS theme variables (--color-*) — never hardcoded colors
- Control flow: @if / @for — never *ngIf / *ngFor
- Components: always standalone: true
- Inputs: input() / input.required() — never @Input()
- Outputs: output() — never @Output()
- Template inline — never templateUrl
- Protected for template fields, private for internal logic
